31453691091969555.jpg\" type=\"photo\" data-is-alt-modified=\"true\" width=\"768\" height=\"512\"></a></p><p>Microsoft also launched the upgraded version of&nbsp;Windows 8.1 in October 2013. It is expected that the first update of&nbsp;Windows 8.1 will be released next April.</p>', 1, '2024-12-09 11:26:39', '2024-12-10 16:04:34', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Computer', 'images/Thp3kznq9n6mlIDvHdRhEJLU5uqlimVOO45YohxV.jpg', 'Will not turning off a Windows computer for a long time cause the system to malfunction?');
