-align:center;width:591.797px;\">&nbsp;</figcaption></figure></div><p>For photography enthusiasts, the Neo7 is equipped with a 50-megapixel Sony OIS main camera and an 8-megapixel lens on the rear, along with a 16-megapixel front camera for high-quality selfies. Inside, the phone uses the MediaTek Dimensity 9300+ chip, promising powerful processing power, ideal for gaming, multitasking and running heavy graphics applications smoothly. In terms of connectivity, the phone supports dual-frequency GPS, 3-frequency Beidou, has an infrared port, NFC, linear motor and dual stereo speakers, ensuring a comprehensive feature set for the modern user.</p><p>Realme Neo7 will have three attractive colors: Starship Edition, Meteorite Black and Submarine, with a starting price of ≤2,499 yuan (equivalent to about 8.71 million VND). With an innovative design, huge battery and waterproof feature, this product is designed for those who are looking for a durable smartphone with strong, stable performance.</p>', 1, '2024-12-09 11:38:20', '2024-12-10 16:04:34', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'realme Neo7', 'images/xpo1M2Uy61EWLoEkBR1k3HzzMckRPFkmuS25nZZi.jpg', 'On December 11, realme will officially launch the realme Neo7 phone. That\'s why recently, information about this product has been continuously shared on websites.'),
(23, 1, 11, 'Rolex Oyster Perpetual Lady-Datejust: Sparkling song', '<p>Rolex Oyster Perpetual Lady-Datejust, as a promise with time, has accompanied elegant ladies since 1957. Converging the essence of the Datejust watch line - a symbol of style and top technology tall since its launch in 1945 – this feminine version is a whisper of sophisticated female beauty. With a small size of 28 mm, Lady-Datejust cleverly hugs the slender wrist, marking every memorable moment.</p><p>Lady-Datejust is present in countless versions, but the most special are the watches decorated with sparkling diamonds. For example, the masterpiece Rolex Oyster Perpetual Lady-Datejust, crafted from 18 ct Everose gold, features a diamond-encrusted dial and President bracelet, creating a fascinating work of chronological art.</p><figure class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\" style=\"--tw-backdrop-blur:;--tw-backdrop-brightness:;--tw-backdrop-contrast:;--tw-backdrop-grayscale:;--tw-backdrop-hue-rotate:;--tw-backdrop-invert:;--tw-backdrop-opacity:;--tw-backdrop-saturate:;--tw-backdrop-sepia:;--tw-bg-opacity:1;--tw-blur:;--tw-border-spacing-x:0;--tw-border-spacing-y:0;--tw-brightness:;--tw-contain-layout:;--tw-contain-paint:;--tw-contain-size:;--tw-contain-style:;--tw-contrast:;--tw-drop-shadow:;--tw-gradient-from-position:;--tw-gradient-to-position:;--tw-gradient-via-position:;--tw-grayscale:;--tw-hue-rotate:;--tw-invert:;--tw-numeric-figure:;--tw-numeric-fraction:;--tw-numeric-spacing:;--tw-ordinal:;--tw-pan-x:;--tw-pan-y:;--tw-pinch-zoom:;--tw-ring-color:rgba(59,130,246,.5);--tw-ring-inset:;--tw-ring-offset-color:#fff;--tw-ring-offset-shadow:0 0 #0000;--tw-ring-offset-width:0px;--tw-ring-shadow:0 0 #0000;--tw-rotate:0;--tw-saturate:;--tw-scale-x:1;--tw-scale-y:1;--tw-scroll-snap-strictness:proximity;--tw-sepia:;--tw-shadow-colored:0 0 #0000;--tw-shadow:0 0 #0000;--tw-skew-x:0;--tw-skew-y:0;--tw-slashed-zero:;--tw-translate-x:0;--tw-translate-y:0;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(244 244