(27, NULL, 7, 26, 'Loa Bluetooth SOUNARC P1', 20, 'SOUNARC P1 Bluetooth Speaker combines modern design, powerful sound, and exceptional portability, delivering high-quality audio experiences wherever you go.\r\n\r\nKey Features:\r\n360-Degree Immersive Sound: Equipped with advanced surround sound technology, the SOUNARC P1 delivers rich, clear audio with deep bass, perfect for parties or daily use.\r\nSleek Design: Crafted with premium materials, the speaker is dustproof and water-resistant with an IPX5 rating, making it suitable for both indoor and outdoor use.\r\nBluetooth 5.0 Connectivity: Ensures a stable and fast connection with low power consumption, offering a range of up to 10 meters.\r\nLong Battery Life: A high-capacity battery allows up to 12 hours of continuous playtime on a single charge, ideal for long trips or all-day use.\r\nConvenient Controls: Integrated buttons on the speaker let you easily switch tracks, adjust volume, and control playback without needing your phone.\r\nVersatile Input Options: Supports Bluetooth, AUX, and a memory card slot, giving you multiple ways to enjoy your favorite music.\r\nThe SOUNARC P1 is the perfect choice for those seeking a blend of premium sound quality and versatile usage. With its affordable price, it’s a must-have for music enthusiasts looking to elevate their listening experience.', '[{\"name\":\"Brand\",\"option\":\"SOUNARC\"},{\"name\":\"Capacity\",\"option\":\"80 Hz - 20 kHz\"},{\"name\":\"Machine line\",\"option\":\"Loa Bluetooth SOUNARC P1\"},{\"name\":\"Status\",\"option\":\"ussed\"},{\"name\":\"Color\",\"option\":\"white\"},{\"name\":\"Origin\",\"option\":\"Viet Nam\"}]', 1, 1, 6, '2024-12-09 13:39:08', '2025-01-08 13:39:08', '2024-12-09 13:09:21', '2024-12-09 13:39:08', NULL, '68 Ngô Thị nhậm, Tỉnh Bắc Giang, Huyện Hiệp Hòa, Xã Danh Thắng', 17, '0941518881'),
(28, NULL, 7, 27, 'Smart Tivi Samsung UHD 4K 65 inch UA65AU7700', 1000, 'Samsung Smart TV UHD 4K 65 inch UA65AU7700\r\nThe Samsung Smart TV UA65AU7700 delivers an exceptional entertainment experience with its stunning 4K resolution, sleek design, and advanced smart features, making it a perfect addition to any modern living space.\r\n\r\nKey Features:\r\nUHD 4K Resolution: Provides four times the detail of Full HD with vibrant colors and sharp visuals in every frame.\r\nPurColor Technology: Enhances color accuracy, delivering lifelike and vivid images.\r\nCrystal 4K Processor: Optimizes picture quality and color dynamically for smooth and vivid viewing experiences.\r\nAirSlim Design: Ultra-slim and elegant, seamlessly blending into any interior decor.\r\nTizen OS: User-friendly interface with access to a wide range of apps like Netflix, YouTube, Disney+, and more.\r\nMulti View Feature: Allows you to split the screen and watch content from the TV and your smartphone simultaneously.\r\nVoice Control: Integrated Bixby assistant and compatibility with Google Assistant for effortless TV operation.\r\nVersatile Connectivity: Supports Bluetooth, Wi-Fi, HDMI, and USB for quick and flexible connections to other devices.\r\nSpecifications:\r\nScreen Size: 65 inches\r\nResolution: 3840 x 2160 pixels (4K)\r\nAudio Output: 20W with Dolby Digital Plus support\r\nPorts: 3 HDMI, 1 USB, LAN, Optical, Bluetooth 5.0\r\nDimensions (with stand): 1449.6 x 906.6 x 282.1 mm\r\nWeight: 20.9 kg\r\nThe Samsung UA65AU7700 is the ideal choice for your family, offering an immersive entertainment experience with vibrant visuals and superior sound quality.', '[{\"name\":\"Brand\",\"option\":\"Samsung\"},{\"name\":\"Capacity\",\"option\":\"65 in - 3840 x 2160 pixels (4K)\"},{\"name\":\"Machine line\",\"option\":\"Smart Tivi Samsung UHD 4K 65 inch UA65AU7700\"},{\"name\":\"Status\",\"option\":\"Used\"},{\"name\":\"Color\",\"option\":\"White\"},{\"name\":\"Origin\",\"option\":\"Viet Nam\"}]', 0, 1, 