(30, NULL, 7, 32, 'Masstel Smart Hero GO', 1230, 'Masstel Smart Hero GO\r\nThe Masstel Smart Hero GO is a compact yet powerful smartphone designed for users who seek reliability and practicality at an affordable price. Its sleek design, intuitive interface, and essential features make it a great choice for everyday use.\r\n\r\nKey Features:\r\nSleek and Modern Design: A slim, lightweight body with a stylish finish that fits comfortably in your hand.\r\nBright Display: A clear and vibrant screen for comfortable viewing, whether browsing, texting, or watching videos.\r\nEfficient Performance: Powered by a quad-core processor for smooth operation of basic apps and tasks.\r\nExpandable Storage: Offers internal storage with an option to expand via a microSD card to store your favorite photos, videos, and apps.\r\nDual SIM Support: Convenient for managing personal and work numbers in one device.\r\nLong-lasting Battery: A reliable battery life that keeps you connected throughout the day.\r\nAffordable and Accessible: Combines essential features with a budget-friendly price, making it accessible to a wide range of users.\r\nSpecifications:\r\nDisplay: Compact screen with vivid colors (exact dimensions depend on model specifics).\r\nProcessor: Quad-core for efficient multitasking.\r\nCamera: Front and rear cameras for capturing life\'s moments.\r\nConnectivity: Supports 4G, Wi-Fi, Bluetooth, and GPS.\r\nBattery: Long-lasting with moderate usage.\r\nOperating System: Android-based system for a user-friendly experience.\r\nThe Masstel Smart Hero GO is an ideal option for first-time smartphone users or those looking for a secondary device with all the essential functionalities. It’s a smart choice for practical, everyday needs.', '[{\"name\":\"Brand\",\"option\":\"GO\"},{\"name\":\"Capacity\",\"option\":\"Supports 4G, Wi-Fi, Bluetooth, and GPS.\"},{\"name\":\"Machine line\",\"option\":\"Masstel Smart Hero GO\"},{\"name\":\"Status\",\"option\":\"Used\"},{\"name\":\"Color\",\"op