(45, NULL, 11, 31, 'Mainboard Asus Prime H610M-K D4 ( LGA1700 - ATX motherboard - DDR4 )', 10, 'The Asus Prime H610M-K D4 is a reliable and versatile motherboard designed to maximize the performance of Intel 12th and 13th generation processors. With its Micro-ATX form factor, this board offers robust features in a compact size, making it ideal for building efficient and cost-effective systems.\r\n\r\nKey Features:\r\nLGA1700 Socket: Supports the latest Intel 12th Gen Alder Lake and 13th Gen Raptor Lake processors for top-tier performance in multitasking and gaming.\r\nDDR4 Memory Support: Equipped with dual-channel DDR4 slots supporting up to 64GB RAM, ensuring fast and efficient memory operation for smooth performance.\r\nCompact Micro-ATX Design: A space-saving layout that fits into smaller PC cases while retaining essential functionality.\r\nComprehensive Cooling Options: Features hybrid fan headers and ASUS Fan Xpert for effective cooling and system stability.\r\nConnectivity:\r\nStorage: 1 x M.2 slot (PCIe 3.0 x4) and 4 x SATA 6Gb/s ports for flexible storage options.\r\nUSB Ports: Multiple USB ports, including USB 3.2 Gen 1 and USB 2.0 for fast data transfer and device connectivity.\r\nNetworking: Integrated Realtek Gigabit Ethernet ensures stable and reliable internet connectivity.\r\nGraphics Support: Outputs include HDMI 2.1 and D-Sub, providing options for high-definition displays.\r\nEnhanced Durability: Features ASUS 5X Protection III for enhanced longevity, including overvoltage protection, stainless-steel back I/O, and durable components.', '[{\"name\":\"Brand\",\"option\":\"Asus\"},{\"name\":\"Capacity\",\"option\":\"2 x DDR4 DIMM (up to 64GB)\"},{\"name\":\"Machine line\",\"option\":\"Mainboard Asus Prime H610M-K D4 ( LGA1700 - ATX motherboard - DDR4 )\"},{\"name\":\"Status\",\"option\":\"Used\"},{\"name\":\"Color\",\"option\":\"Black\"},{\"name\":\"Origin\",\"option\":\"Viet Nam, China\"}]', 1, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2024-12-10 17:07:22', '2024-12-10