(46, NULL, 11, 31, 'Canon laser LBP6030', 10, 'Canon Laser Printer LBP6030\r\nThe Canon Laser LBP6030 is a compact, energy-efficient, and high-performance monochrome laser printer, designed for small offices or personal use. Its fast printing speed and exceptional quality make it an excellent choice for users who need reliable and efficient document printing.\r\n\r\nKey Features:\r\nCompact Design: Sleek and space-saving, the LBP6030 fits easily on a desk or in tight office spaces.\r\nFast Printing: Prints at a speed of up to 18 pages per minute (ppm) on A4 paper, with the first print out in just 7.8 seconds.\r\nHigh-Quality Output: Produces crisp, clear text and sharp graphics with a resolution of up to 2400 x 600 dpi (with automatic image refinement).\r\nEnergy Efficient: Features Canon’s On-Demand Fixing Technology, which minimizes power consumption and warms up the printer quickly.\r\nQuiet Operation: Operates with minimal noise, ensuring a peaceful workspace.\r\nCost-Effective: Uses Canon’s Cartridge 325, an all-in-one cartridge system that combines toner, drum, and cleaning units for hassle-free maintenance and lower running costs.\r\nUser-Friendly: Easy to set up and operate with a simple interface, making it ideal for non-technical users.', '[{\"name\":\"Brand\",\"option\":\"Canon\"},{\"name\":\"Capacity\",\"option\":\"Up to 2400 x 600 dpi\"},{\"name\":\"Machine line\",\"option\":\"Canon laser LBP6030\"},{\"name\":\"Status\",\"option\":\"Used\"},{\"name\":\"Color\",\"option\":\"White\"},{\"name\":\"Origin\",\"option\":\"Viet Nam, China\"}]', 1, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2024-12-10 17:11:12', '2024-12-10 17:12:52', NULL, '68 Ngô Thị nhậm, Tỉnh Thái Nguyên, Thành phố Sông Công, Xã Bá Xuyên', 1, '0941518881'),
